In order to install FileZilla FTP client, please do the following steps:

1) Open your browser, go to http://filezilla-project.org , and then click on Download FileZilla Client option.

2)  Select the right setup file for your operating system. For Windows, select the recommended version to install it.

3) A pop up window will appear prompting you to either Save or Run the file. Click on Save file option.

4) Once the download is completed, run the installation file.

5) Click on "I Agree" license agreement.


6) A new window for choosing installation option will appear. Select “Anyone who uses this computer” if you want to install FileZilla for all your users or “Only for me” if you only want to install it for yourself. Then click next.
